{"tid":1598371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投行前高層“被離職”，大家一齊幫下法國巴黎銀行處理下手頭上嘅上市申請","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T15:09:25.000Z","uid":219470,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6e5b8480f48774e670a6b3144c20e8ceebfd86","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"事緣：<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2262071/法巴前高層稱已離職+投身民主運動\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2262071%2F%E6%B3%95%E5%B7%B4%E5%89%8D%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%2B%E6%8A%95%E8%BA%AB%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=854832f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2262071/法巴前高層稱已離職+投身民主運動</a><br />\n<br />\n見到法巴咁照顧微博網民嘅感受，搞到我朋友都好想表揚下佢地<br />\n<br />\n特登google下佢地手頭上有咩上市申請，第一個搜索結果就見到：<br />\n<blockquote>曾從美國納斯達克私有化退市的中手游科技集團，昨日第三度衝擊港股新股市場，向港交所遞交招股書，擬在主板上市，中金公司及法巴為其聯席保薦人。該公司曾於去年9月及今年4月向港交所提交上市申請。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n再google一下中手游，竟然發現d咁嘅野:<br />\n<a href=\"http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2014-07-15/21119495461.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftech.sina.com.cn%2Fi%2F2014-07-15%2F21119495461.shtml&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=9872a13b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2014-07-15/21119495461.shtml</a><br />\n<blockquote>霍华德史密斯律师事务所在起诉书中称，中手游发布关于业务和运营方面的虚假/误导性声明，而并未公布一些重大不利事实，尤其是：<span style=\"color: red;\">1)一项贿赂游戏发行商的计划；2)未公布的集团内交易；3)内部控制不充分。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然件事都過左咁多年，但一班黃絲可能會為呢間事大造文章，影響呢間公司嘅上司申請，再間接影響埋法巴嘅收入（有做投行嘅朋友同我講，一單呢d deal法巴分分鐘收到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7位數美金</strong></span>），就算唔可以令到中手游上市收皮，都分分鐘令到法巴工作量大增，接唔到其他生意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以大家千奇唔好同聯交所/證監會打報告，加重法巴工作量，甚至搞到人地無左七位數收入呀</span></strong>"},{"pid":"df403ab57c9d26b5fb2578289ba55db894a51efd","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"2dac57d08377ff7bd5d52ba71dc14f4f43b1b93a","tid":1598371,"uid":43197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5e3f68536a1f30c3f9178c99be747d1c107aff6b","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:54:28.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"121de9a36f1c13b11d50a458e86e5a7c391d3902","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:55:07.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"c50bc26fcd1b6d602c8448678bce129e2f9a7a2d","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"110b46e3c096fe39863c2d2c096e24349084a0a7","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"d4a1dd436675b26f8df3b89cddd41e8643b9843f","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"829700815b6cf3b23b4585114025434e462984f5","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"推7/10"},{"pid":"cbbda83bb5905644fc5780f93b7cc3226c1e6152","tid":1598371,"uid":321642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:58:00.000Z","msg":"P 牌推唔到"},{"pid":"bacb59906a4c9342245e6e60f3d31a7bccfae325","tid":1598371,"uid":219470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:58:38.000Z","msg":"推8/10"},{"pid":"1b56579e8bdbf2a17d55e9fe9d94f3ed04d61750","tid":1598371,"uid":269498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6